{"tid":1753104,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［入嚟笑佢］CY：東山再起","createTime":"2019-11-25T01:26:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T01:33:01.000Z","uid":4599,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"34d1e07cb7759b7766c427b90c93c40b0ff824aa","tid":1753104,"uid":4599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:26:09.000Z","msg":"給所有建制派的區議會候選人，<br />\n勝不驕，敗不餒是競選的不二法則，希望大家繼續做好政治和地區工作，建設香港，服務選民，東山再起。<br />\n<br />\n給所有投票給建制派的選民,<br />\n感謝大家昨日不辭勞苦，長時間排隊投票，昨日投票給建制派的百萬選民，勇敢地用選票向暴力和破壞說不。請大家今後團結一致，全力監察區議員在會內會外的工作。<br />\n<br />\n全香港此時更須冷靜，耐心，一起維護香港長遠和整體利益。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CvasrKZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCvasrKZ.png&h=b140fe51&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a980685acc9fc6868abc3e4c2cfb3374cce4f8b","tid":1753104,"uid":4599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:27:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8234b21b0215394d5073fa63ca4425493b6d24ef","tid":1753104,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:27:40.000Z","msg":"Mk妹果句<br />\n咩輸就陪你東山再起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a051e142b5c95f78afd0d093c578b4c92dc74f81","tid":1753104,"uid":4599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:27:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f357dd621aa22be6d7c4a1a3281ac83ec953ae","tid":1753104,"uid":4599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:28:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f804704858686557aca7439c7f147433f546faa7","tid":1753104,"uid":59447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:28:05.000Z","msg":"佢有競選過?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e60213a5fc14f5ca1968a00fb70ad187c5fe8147","tid":1753104,"uid":315